title: rendering
pid: 696a2294-b6d9-4ac4-b5ac-2a59ee0789cc
body: |2-
  Adorned with an 'is_relationship' glyph.
  Each member appears as a link,
  and the connecting text as ordinary text.
  (Two spaces on either side of each link,
  so that even if the connecting text is empty,
  they are clearly distinct.)
